00:16:23.500 --> 00:16:27.610 align:middle line:84%
We're going to work on undoing
all those unhealthy eating

00:16:27.610 --> 00:16:32.192 align:middle line:84%
habits now and make that
change once and for all.

00:16:32.192 --> 00:16:40.230 align:middle line:90%


00:16:40.230 --> 00:16:44.100 align:middle line:84%
We all start off our lives
with normal thinking patterns

00:16:44.100 --> 00:16:46.710 align:middle line:90%
around food.

00:16:46.710 --> 00:16:49.035 align:middle line:84%
But somehow, your
thinking has changed.

00:16:49.035 --> 00:16:52.480 align:middle line:90%


00:16:52.480 --> 00:16:55.300 align:middle line:84%
I'd like you now to have a
think about whether you're

00:16:55.300 --> 00:17:02.200 align:middle line:84%
eating to make yourself
happy, or is it boredom.

00:17:02.200 --> 00:17:06.460 align:middle line:84%
Think about how you went
from being normal about food

00:17:06.460 --> 00:17:09.110 align:middle line:90%
to not being in control anymore.

00:17:09.110 --> 00:17:14.880 align:middle line:90%


00:17:14.880 --> 00:17:20.319 align:middle line:84%
I'd like you now to think about
why you want to lose weight.

00:17:20.319 --> 00:17:22.650 align:middle line:84%
You know that losing
weight for someone else

00:17:22.650 --> 00:17:28.410 align:middle line:84%
is not going to be enough
of motivation for you.

00:17:28.410 --> 00:17:31.110 align:middle line:84%
Losing weight for
someone to love you,

00:17:31.110 --> 00:17:35.400 align:middle line:84%
for people to like you is
completely the wrong reason

00:17:35.400 --> 00:17:39.300 align:middle line:84%
and you won't see any
long-term results there.

00:17:39.300 --> 00:17:41.970 align:middle line:84%
This decision must
be completely yours.

00:17:41.970 --> 00:17:50.080 align:middle line:90%


00:17:50.080 --> 00:17:54.550 align:middle line:84%
Losing weight permanently
and healthily will only

00:17:54.550 --> 00:17:58.630 align:middle line:84%
be possible if you're doing
it for the right reason.

00:17:58.630 --> 00:18:02.605 align:middle line:84%
The reason should be for
yourself, not for anyone else.

00:18:02.605 --> 00:18:05.800 align:middle line:90%


00:18:05.800 --> 00:18:09.250 align:middle line:84%
You know that you need to
change your habit of thinking

00:18:09.250 --> 00:18:16.630 align:middle line:84%
around food And once you change
your thinking around food,

00:18:16.630 --> 00:18:19.015 align:middle line:84%
the actions around
food will change.

00:18:19.015 --> 00:18:21.680 align:middle line:90%


00:18:21.680 --> 00:18:25.700 align:middle line:84%
The action of overeating
or eating the wrong foods

00:18:25.700 --> 00:18:27.750 align:middle line:90%
will go forever.

00:18:27.750 --> 00:18:31.700 align:middle line:84%
But first we need to change your
habit of thinking around food.

00:18:31.700 --> 00:18:38.210 align:middle line:90%


00:18:38.210 --> 00:18:43.040 align:middle line:84%
Once you've broken that habitual
thinking which your mind has

00:18:43.040 --> 00:18:48.410 align:middle line:84%
created, then you'll soon
see how your actions will in

00:18:48.410 --> 00:18:49.820 align:middle line:90%
turn change too.

00:18:49.820 --> 00:18:53.670 align:middle line:90%


00:18:53.670 --> 00:18:58.840 align:middle line:84%
You know that diet pills don't
change your thinking, which

00:18:58.840 --> 00:19:01.330 align:middle line:84%
is why the minute people
come off their diet

00:19:01.330 --> 00:19:06.850 align:middle line:84%
pills their thinking habits
of food, of eating too much,

00:19:06.850 --> 00:19:12.350 align:middle line:84%
or eating junk food comes
straight back again,

00:19:12.350 --> 00:19:17.330 align:middle line:84%
and maybe they put the weight
straight back on again.

00:19:17.330 --> 00:19:21.850 align:middle line:84%
So we really need to change
your thinking around food now,

00:19:21.850 --> 00:19:23.660 align:middle line:84%
and you're ready to
make that change.

00:19:23.660 --> 00:19:28.230 align:middle line:90%


00:19:28.230 --> 00:19:33.030 align:middle line:84%
I'd like you now to think about
when you were a little child

00:19:33.030 --> 00:19:37.960 align:middle line:84%
and you were offered a slice
of cake, perhaps at a party.

00:19:37.960 --> 00:19:42.460 align:middle line:84%
You may have taken a bite
and then run off to play

00:19:42.460 --> 00:19:47.080 align:middle line:84%
and perhaps come back for
another bite, so easily

00:19:47.080 --> 00:19:50.560 align:middle line:84%
distracted, not in
a rush to finish

00:19:50.560 --> 00:19:54.840 align:middle line:84%
the cake, no worrying about
the cake disappearing.

00:19:54.840 --> 00:19:57.520 align:middle line:90%


00:19:57.520 --> 00:20:01.450 align:middle line:84%
We're all born with the
same thinking around food.

00:20:01.450 --> 00:20:03.760 align:middle line:84%
Just like when you
were this little child,

00:20:03.760 --> 00:20:06.610 align:middle line:84%
you didn't worry
about food being

00:20:06.610 --> 00:20:11.530 align:middle line:84%
a rarity, about that slice
of cake being a naughty food,

00:20:11.530 --> 00:20:14.530 align:middle line:90%
so you ran off and came back.

00:20:14.530 --> 00:20:16.520 align:middle line:90%
It was no big deal.

00:20:16.520 --> 00:20:19.500 align:middle line:84%
In fact, food wasn't
the main focus your day.

00:20:19.500 --> 00:20:22.160 align:middle line:90%


00:20:22.160 --> 00:20:25.130 align:middle line:84%
Something happened in your
life and now your thinking

00:20:25.130 --> 00:20:29.180 align:middle line:84%
has changed and you've
reframed those foods,

00:20:29.180 --> 00:20:32.140 align:middle line:84%
and now food has become
your main focus of your day.

00:20:32.140 --> 00:20:38.270 align:middle line:90%


00:20:38.270 --> 00:20:40.220 align:middle line:84%
And one of the
main problems here

00:20:40.220 --> 00:20:43.820 align:middle line:84%
is that the more you
resist certain foods,

00:20:43.820 --> 00:20:45.964 align:middle line:90%
the more you want them.

00:20:45.964 --> 00:20:48.660 align:middle line:90%


00:20:48.660 --> 00:20:51.410 align:middle line:84%
And we really need to
change your thinking here.

00:20:51.410 --> 00:20:54.240 align:middle line:90%


00:20:54.240 --> 00:20:56.700 align:middle line:84%
There will be no
more resisting foods.

00:20:56.700 --> 00:20:59.520 align:middle line:84%
You almost want to be
indifferent to food,

00:20:59.520 --> 00:21:01.650 align:middle line:90%
to be disinterested.

00:21:01.650 --> 00:21:05.770 align:middle line:84%
It's no longer the
focus of your day.

00:21:05.770 --> 00:21:09.780 align:middle line:84%
You no longer tell yourself you
can't have that slice of cake,

00:21:09.780 --> 00:21:13.590 align:middle line:84%
you can't have those
biscuits or chocolates.

00:21:13.590 --> 00:21:19.260 align:middle line:84%
Instead, you tell yourself
that you can have those foods.

00:21:19.260 --> 00:21:22.770 align:middle line:84%
But you can have them
tomorrow or the day

00:21:22.770 --> 00:21:26.140 align:middle line:90%
after or later, just not now.

00:21:26.140 --> 00:21:30.820 align:middle line:90%


00:21:30.820 --> 00:21:33.100 align:middle line:84%
By thinking in this
way, you're not

00:21:33.100 --> 00:21:38.110 align:middle line:84%
resisting foods and therefore
creating even bigger motivation

00:21:38.110 --> 00:21:39.150 align:middle line:90%
to eat that food.

00:21:39.150 --> 00:21:45.310 align:middle line:90%


00:21:45.310 --> 00:21:48.610 align:middle line:84%
From now on, your
subconscious mind no longer

00:21:48.610 --> 00:21:52.690 align:middle line:84%
fights and resists
unhealthy foods,

00:21:52.690 --> 00:21:56.950 align:middle line:84%
as this will only increase
your motivation for it.

00:21:56.950 --> 00:22:00.700 align:middle line:90%
It will consume you.

00:22:00.700 --> 00:22:02.830 align:middle line:84%
From now on, your
brain will only

00:22:02.830 --> 00:22:08.500 align:middle line:84%
want healthy, nutritious,
and tasty food.

00:22:08.500 --> 00:22:11.260 align:middle line:84%
You're no longer
interested in sugar

00:22:11.260 --> 00:22:14.110 align:middle line:90%
and pesticides and colorings.

00:22:14.110 --> 00:22:21.220 align:middle line:84%
You only crave healthy, whole
foods that fuel your body.

00:22:21.220 --> 00:22:26.170 align:middle line:84%
From now on, if you see a
cake or unhealthy treat,

00:22:26.170 --> 00:22:29.150 align:middle line:84%
you may feel like
you would love one

00:22:29.150 --> 00:22:32.380 align:middle line:84%
but you realize that you love
fitting into your clothes

00:22:32.380 --> 00:22:34.540 align:middle line:90%
even more.

00:22:34.540 --> 00:22:36.725 align:middle line:84%
You choose yourself
as a priority.

00:22:36.725 --> 00:22:39.310 align:middle line:90%


00:22:39.310 --> 00:22:44.590 align:middle line:84%
You know that you can have that
treat but you choose not to.

00:22:44.590 --> 00:22:47.080 align:middle line:90%
You don't overthink it.

00:22:47.080 --> 00:22:49.630 align:middle line:84%
You simply tell
yourself you can have it

00:22:49.630 --> 00:22:54.320 align:middle line:84%
and you can have it tomorrow
or later or next week.

00:22:54.320 --> 00:22:58.450 align:middle line:84%
But right now, you
choose a healthy option

00:22:58.450 --> 00:23:03.340 align:middle line:84%
and you feel pride as you
eat that healthy alternative.

00:23:03.340 --> 00:23:06.910 align:middle line:84%
You feel satisfaction
and confidence

00:23:06.910 --> 00:23:12.280 align:middle line:84%
as you fit into your clothes
much more comfortably now.

00:23:12.280 --> 00:23:14.480 align:middle line:84%
And those feelings
of satisfaction

00:23:14.480 --> 00:23:17.710 align:middle line:84%
grow stronger and
stronger as you

00:23:17.710 --> 00:23:20.140 align:middle line:84%
start to see the
changes in your body.

00:23:20.140 --> 00:23:27.820 align:middle line:90%


00:23:27.820 --> 00:23:33.220 align:middle line:84%
From now on, you feel the
freedom of not always obsessing

00:23:33.220 --> 00:23:36.280 align:middle line:90%
over food.

00:23:36.280 --> 00:23:41.260 align:middle line:84%
You love your body, and you're
excited about eating better

00:23:41.260 --> 00:23:47.160 align:middle line:84%
food, about looking better,
feeling and looking younger

00:23:47.160 --> 00:23:50.714 align:middle line:90%
and having much more energy.

00:23:50.714 --> 00:23:53.610 align:middle line:84%
You no longer want
that guilty feeling

00:23:53.610 --> 00:23:58.050 align:middle line:84%
after you've eaten too much
or too much of the wrong food.

00:23:58.050 --> 00:23:59.880 align:middle line:84%
You're done with
that feeling now.

00:23:59.880 --> 00:24:04.380 align:middle line:90%


