If you know that
you're going to be

00:24:06.210 --> 00:24:10.110 align:middle line:84%
craving something at
a certain time of day,

00:24:10.110 --> 00:24:14.400 align:middle line:84%
craving something sweet to
eat, and from now on you

00:24:14.400 --> 00:24:17.310 align:middle line:84%
make sure that you have
a healthy alternative

00:24:17.310 --> 00:24:20.910 align:middle line:84%
ready to go, ready to
get rid of that craving.

00:24:20.910 --> 00:24:24.810 align:middle line:90%


00:24:24.810 --> 00:24:30.680 align:middle line:84%
You know that cutting
something out won't work

00:24:30.680 --> 00:24:33.940 align:middle line:84%
and it will only make
it worse and motivate

00:24:33.940 --> 00:24:36.160 align:middle line:90%
you to eat that food even more.

00:24:36.160 --> 00:24:40.510 align:middle line:90%


00:24:40.510 --> 00:24:42.450 align:middle line:84%
You're no longer
going to yo-yo diet.

00:24:42.450 --> 00:24:46.520 align:middle line:90%


00:24:46.520 --> 00:24:50.960 align:middle line:84%
No more rewarding yourself
for losing the weight

00:24:50.960 --> 00:24:54.210 align:middle line:90%
with other foods.

00:24:54.210 --> 00:24:57.140 align:middle line:84%
No more rewarding yourself
with ice cream or chocolate

00:24:57.140 --> 00:24:58.505 align:middle line:90%
if you lose a few pounds.

00:24:58.505 --> 00:25:04.460 align:middle line:90%


00:25:04.460 --> 00:25:07.250 align:middle line:84%
You're depriving
yourself of those foods

00:25:07.250 --> 00:25:10.700 align:middle line:84%
and then punishing yourself
with bad foods again,

00:25:10.700 --> 00:25:14.835 align:middle line:84%
and you want this vicious
circle to end once and for all.

00:25:14.835 --> 00:25:18.160 align:middle line:90%


00:25:18.160 --> 00:25:24.870 align:middle line:84%
You're aware of portions and
you stop when you feel full.

00:25:24.870 --> 00:25:30.540 align:middle line:84%
You no longer want to feel
so full that you feel sick.

00:25:30.540 --> 00:25:33.090 align:middle line:84%
You realize that
any happiness you

00:25:33.090 --> 00:25:40.620 align:middle line:84%
feel after eating those
foods is false happiness,

