and you no longer want to
feel that false happiness

00:25:44.250 --> 00:25:46.080 align:middle line:90%
and you stop this habit now.

00:25:46.080 --> 00:25:49.710 align:middle line:90%


00:25:49.710 --> 00:25:53.230 align:middle line:84%
You have respect and
love for your body,

00:25:53.230 --> 00:25:57.288 align:middle line:84%
and you no longer want to
hate it or punish it anymore.

00:25:57.288 --> 00:26:05.430 align:middle line:90%


