You don't push yourself to do
exercise that you don't enjoy,

00:26:09.990 --> 00:26:13.170 align:middle line:90%
as this won't work long term.

00:26:13.170 --> 00:26:17.040 align:middle line:84%
Instead, you find something
you're interested in,

00:26:17.040 --> 00:26:21.030 align:middle line:84%
that you fall in love with,
that you're passionate about,

00:26:21.030 --> 00:26:23.820 align:middle line:90%
that makes you happy.

00:26:23.820 --> 00:26:27.030 align:middle line:84%
And because you enjoy it,
you're much more interested

00:26:27.030 --> 00:26:30.330 align:middle line:84%
in it and you're much
more likely to keep

00:26:30.330 --> 00:26:33.072 align:middle line:84%
it going and seeing
results from doing it.

00:26:33.072 --> 00:26:36.520 align:middle line:90%


00:26:36.520 --> 00:26:39.400 align:middle line:84%
And your body is loving
the new healthier way

00:26:39.400 --> 00:26:45.850 align:middle line:84%
of eating and the movement
that it's experiencing.

00:26:45.850 --> 00:26:50.400 align:middle line:84%
You're now going to
choose to eat healthily.

00:26:50.400 --> 00:26:54.200 align:middle line:84%
There's no forcing your body to
do what it doesn't want to do.

00:26:54.200 --> 00:26:56.890 align:middle line:90%


00:26:56.890 --> 00:27:00.340 align:middle line:84%
You remember that motivation
will increase if you

