And if you don't
enjoy healthy foods,

00:27:09.860 --> 00:27:15.920 align:middle line:84%
then you need to retrain your
taste buds, slowly but surely.

00:27:15.920 --> 00:27:19.580 align:middle line:90%
And you can do this in time.

00:27:19.580 --> 00:27:21.754 align:middle line:90%
And you're excited to do this.

00:27:21.754 --> 00:27:24.410 align:middle line:90%


00:27:24.410 --> 00:27:27.380 align:middle line:84%
And you start by taking
a small bite of something

00:27:27.380 --> 00:27:29.870 align:middle line:90%
new every day.

