And after 10 days, you will
have changed your taste buds

00:27:33.140 --> 00:27:37.310 align:middle line:84%
and you'll start to love the
new fresh, healthy flavors.

00:27:37.310 --> 00:27:42.150 align:middle line:90%


00:27:42.150 --> 00:27:46.950 align:middle line:84%
Your whole new way of
thinking is about choice,

00:27:46.950 --> 00:27:51.120 align:middle line:84%
and you choose to
leave that biscuit.

00:27:51.120 --> 00:27:54.840 align:middle line:84%
You choose to step away
from any foods that

00:27:54.840 --> 00:27:58.250 align:middle line:90%
aren't considered healthy.

00:27:58.250 --> 00:28:02.930 align:middle line:84%
You know you can have them
later but not right now.

00:28:02.930 --> 00:28:05.110 align:middle line:84%
Tell yourself you
can have them later.

00:28:05.110 --> 00:28:08.000 align:middle line:90%


00:28:08.000 --> 00:28:10.520 align:middle line:84%
And by doing this,
there's no resistance.

00:28:10.520 --> 00:28:13.700 align:middle line:84%
You're not increasing
that motivation.

00:28:13.700 --> 00:28:15.170 align:middle line:90%
You're tricking your mind.

00:28:15.170 --> 00:28:18.230 align:middle line:84%
You're using your
mind's ability.

00:28:18.230 --> 00:28:21.260 align:middle line:84%
You choose different
items of food.

00:28:21.260 --> 00:28:24.710 align:middle line:90%
You choose to be slimmer.

00:28:24.710 --> 00:28:29.630 align:middle line:84%
You know that right now your
weight isn't making you happy.

00:28:29.630 --> 00:28:31.730 align:middle line:84%
And you know that
now is the time

00:28:31.730 --> 00:28:34.110 align:middle line:84%
to work on reframing
of food here.

00:28:34.110 --> 00:28:39.310 align:middle line:90%


