You're choosing to go
to the gym or choosing

00:28:43.180 --> 00:28:45.520 align:middle line:90%
to go for a fast walk.

00:28:45.520 --> 00:28:47.750 align:middle line:84%
Whatever it is that
works for your body,

00:28:47.750 --> 00:28:50.770 align:middle line:90%
you're making these choices.

00:28:50.770 --> 00:28:53.770 align:middle line:90%
Choosing to eat healthily.

00:28:53.770 --> 00:28:58.930 align:middle line:84%
No forcing your body to do
what it doesn't want to do.

00:28:58.930 --> 00:29:01.510 align:middle line:84%
You remember that if
you feel like you really

00:29:01.510 --> 00:29:09.760 align:middle line:84%
do want a treat and no healthy
alternative is available,

00:29:09.760 --> 00:29:14.710 align:middle line:84%
you know that you can
have the odd treat.

