You ideally aim for
80% healthy foods,

00:29:18.880 --> 00:29:22.960 align:middle line:84%
and the other 20% is for you
to have a treat every now

00:29:22.960 --> 00:29:27.520 align:middle line:84%
and then, but it's controlled
and you do not go overboard.

00:29:27.520 --> 00:29:32.140 align:middle line:90%


