To help you make these
changes, you no longer

00:29:35.980 --> 00:29:38.530 align:middle line:84%
keep these treats of
sugar in your home.

00:29:38.530 --> 00:29:40.593 align:middle line:90%
You get them out of sight.

00:29:40.593 --> 00:29:44.560 align:middle line:84%
You know that if you
can see those foods,

00:29:44.560 --> 00:29:47.270 align:middle line:90%
you'll want them even more.

00:29:47.270 --> 00:29:49.682 align:middle line:84%
So you no longer keep
them in your home.

00:29:49.682 --> 00:29:52.520 align:middle line:90%


00:29:52.520 --> 00:29:57.410 align:middle line:84%
And you know that sugar is
one of the most harmful toxins

00:29:57.410 --> 00:29:59.310 align:middle line:90%
and is a poison for your body.

00:29:59.310 --> 00:30:02.570 align:middle line:90%


00:30:02.570 --> 00:30:05.060 align:middle line:84%
You know that fats
are safe, those

00:30:05.060 --> 00:30:10.620 align:middle line:84%
good fats in the form of nuts
and avocados or oily fish,

00:30:10.620 --> 00:30:13.190 align:middle line:90%
and you're not afraid of fat.

