But sugar is something you very
much stay away from from now

00:30:17.000 --> 00:30:19.910 align:middle line:90%
on.

00:30:19.910 --> 00:30:22.760 align:middle line:84%
Remember, there's no forcing
your body to do anything.

00:30:22.760 --> 00:30:26.360 align:middle line:84%
You're simply
making that choice.

00:30:26.360 --> 00:30:29.120 align:middle line:90%
You're choosing to be healthy.

